            "heading": "CONTACT CAPITTEN ",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>To contact us, simply send an email to hello@capitten.com. Our customer service team is committed to responding within 24 hours on business days (Monday to Friday, from 9:00 to 18:00). We appreciate your inquiries and will be happy to assist you as soon as possible.</p>",
            "page": ""
