            "heading": "INTERNATIONAL AVAILABILITY ",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>At Capitten, we work to expand our legacy worldwide. Stay informed by subscribing to our newsletter or following us on social media to know when we will be available in your country.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_zz9dAr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE FOR MY ORDER TO ARRIVE?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Once your order is ready, you will receive a confirmation email with the details and a tracking link. From that moment, delivery will take a maximum of 6 business days.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WaPfpC": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT ARE THE REQUIREMENTS TO RETURN A PRODUCT? ",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>You have 15 calendar days from the date of receipt to request a return. The product must be unused and in perfect condition. You must also keep the original tags (clothing/footwear) and return it in its original packaging.</p>",
